. A. Dytso, M. Cardone, I. Zieder, [https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/9874834/ ``High-Noise Asymptotics of the Ziv-Zakai Bound,"] to appear in  /IEEE Signal Processing Letters/.
. M. Fauß,  A. Dytso, H. V.  Poor, [https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0165168420304618?dgcid=rss_sd_all ``A Variational Interpretation of the Cramer-Rao Bound,"]   /Signal Processing, Elsevier/,  Vol. 182, 2021.
