. A. Dytso, M. Fauß, H. V. Poor, [https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/9625998 "Bayesian Risk with Bregman Loss: A Cramer-Rao Type Bound and Linear Estimation,"] /IEEE Transactions on Information Theory/, Vol.~68, No.~3, March 2022.
